Yael Cohen Braun (amuru na Nọvemba 4, 1986) bu onye azụmahịa ahia South Africa na Canada, na onye so wee tọọ ntọala nke 'Fuck Cancer', otu ahuike na-aru oru maka nchoputa na mgbochi nke oria cancer
A mụrụ Yael Cohen na South Africa, site na ezinụlọ ndị Juu
Nna ya, David Cohen, rụrụ ọrụ dị ka onye ọchụnta ego mmanụ na ngwuputa na Gold Wheaton Gold Corp, Northern Orion Resources na ụlọ ọrụ abụọ ndị ọzọ sitere n'okike
Ọ gara Mahadum nke British Columbia ebe ọ nwetara nzere BA na Sayensị Ọchịchị na 2008
Mgbe ọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ, ọ gara n'ihu na-arụ ọrụ n'ihe gbasara ego
Cohen Braun malitere Fuck Cancer na 2009 mgbe a chọpụtachara nne ya nwere ọrịa kansa nke ara
Fuck Cancer na-achọ ikọwara ndi mmadu ozi site na mgbasa ozi ọha na eze ka ha nwee mkparịta ụka gbasara nchọpụta mmalite na oke mmata banyere ọrịa kansa
Na 2016, Fuck Cancer jikọrọ aka na onye mmebe ọla bụ Jennifer Fisher na ejiji wearables iji kwado ndị ọrịa kansa metụtara
Na 2018, Cohen Braun sonyeere Bumble dị ka onye ndụmọdụ dị elu
Cohen Braun ejirila ego kwado mgbasa ozi onye isi ala na senate nke Cory Booker
Cohen Braun na di ya mgbe ahụ Scooter Braun malitere nkwado ego maka Kamala Harris n'oge ntuli aka nke otu ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị Democratic n'afọ 2020
Cohen Braun lụrụ onye njikwa egwu America Scooter Braun na Julaị 6, 2014, na Whistler, British Columbia
N’ọnwa Julaị afọ 2021, a kọrọ na di na nwunye ahụ kewapụrụ
Braun gbara akwụkwọ maka ịgba alụkwaghịm na Julaị 21, 2021
